  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/05d24baa464622cea6756d156f580530.avif?t=1774114697\" width=576 height=194 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Crawl Tactics combines classic turn-based tactics with roguelike progression. In Dungeon Mode, face challenging, ever-changing encounters as you explore procedurally generated maps. In Quest Mode, develop your village, train your mercenaries, and defend against growing enemy invasions.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/148dfcf487ecee7bcbceb6e2ff944f81.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/148dfcf487ecee7bcbceb6e2ff944f81.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/562d902440590f064631f290f2097ae9.avif?t=1774114697\" width=448 height=77 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>More of a fully fledged Tactical RPG battle than a puzzle game!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/345e54a1c4714595a66a806c24b4c1ad.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/345e54a1c4714595a66a806c24b4c1ad.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/345e54a1c4714595a66a806c24b4c1ad.mp4?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Crawl Tactics is not a puzzle-like tactical game focused on finding one correct solution, but a turn-based strategy RPG forfans of classic, orthodox SRPGs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can enjoy deep tactical gameplay that considers height differences, unit facing, weather, terrain, and more.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Combat that uses the environment and traps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/f5ba9b8be11edf8889c3f13c3006c084.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/f5ba9b8be11edf8889c3f13c3006c084.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/f5ba9b8be11edf8889c3f13c3006c084.mp4?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traps and terrain affect both you and your enemies. Set grass on fire, electrocute enemies standing on water, or ignite poison clouds.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various interactions are possible through pushing/throwing objects and units. Push enemies off high ground or into blade traps, or roll boulders to hit them.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also activate cannons or crossbow traps to damage distant enemies, and all traps can trigger in chains for satisfying results.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Growth, customization, and building the party you want</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/b1990984dec22b65fc71137add88d5b9.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/b1990984dec22b65fc71137add88d5b9.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can freely customize skills, equipment, classes, techniques, and appearance.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even after clearing the main dungeon, you can continue developing your characters through New Game Plus and Reverse, which allows you to reset classes even after advancing to higher tiers.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a solo party to an 8-member battle party, you can build any party composition you want.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging and ever-changing Dungeon Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/3466e965fa9195d9967a4aef18383f7c.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/3466e965fa9195d9967a4aef18383f7c.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/3466e965fa9195d9967a4aef18383f7c.mp4?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon Mode lets you explore dungeons composed of multiple rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Both the dungeons and the battlefields within them are procedurally generated, providing challenging and varied experiences.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ruins, caves, catacombs, forests—each features unique climates, monsters, and environments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every dungeon may include hostile or friendly NPCs, special mercenaries or valuable items, and unique events such as siege battles or defense missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Quest Mode focused on village building and character development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/374d376d03395e6d3c3f64e4f1973eca.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/374d376d03395e6d3c3f64e4f1973eca.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/374d376d03395e6d3c3f64e4f1973eca.mp4?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Quest Mode, you expand your village by constructing buildings each turn and hire multiple mercenaries, sending whichever ones you choose on the quests you want.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rewards differ depending on the type of quest you undertake each turn, and you can also choose higher difficulties, allowing as much grinding as you prefer.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through village events where monsters invade at set intervals, you can engage in larger-scale battles than in standard quests.</p></li></ul>",
