li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can also activate cannons or crossbow traps to damage distant enemies, and all traps can trigger in chains for satisfying results.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Growth, customization, and building the party you want</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/b1990984dec22b65fc71137add88d5b9.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/b1990984dec22b65fc71137add88d5b9.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can freely customize skills, equipment, classes, techniques, and appearance.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Even after clearing the main dungeon, you can continue developing your characters through New Game Plus and Reverse, which allows you to reset classes even after advancing to higher tiers.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From a solo party to an 8-member battle party, you can build any party composition you want.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Challenging and ever-changing Dungeon Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/3466e965fa9195d9967a4aef18383f7c.poster.avif?t=1774114697\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1290750/extras/3466e965fa9195d9967a4aef18383f7c.webm?t=1774114697\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"htt